trans-unit.source: An abstract base class from which all classes that represent proposed changes to a running workflow instance must derive.
trans-unit.target: En abstrakt basklass som alla klasser som representerar föreslagna ändringar till en arbetsflödesinstans som körs måste vara härledd.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.WorkflowChangeAction"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Implementeras i en härledd klass initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.WorkflowChangeAction"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, applies the changes to the root <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass, tillämpar ändringarna till roten <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the root <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> was updated with the added <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the root <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> is a null reference (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om roten <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> har uppdaterats med den tillagda <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref>, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om roten <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> är en null-referens (<xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""> </xref> i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, validates the changes and returns a <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationErrorCollection"></xref> that contains any errors.
trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass validerar ändringarna och returnerar ett <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationErrorCollection"> </xref> som innehåller några fel.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> upon which to validate the changes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> som du vill verifiera ändringarna.

trans-unit.source: activityInstance is a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: activityInstanceär en null-referens ( i Visual Basic).
